<h4><a href="https://www.rec.uk.com/good-recruitment-campaign">Good Recruitment Campaign</a></h4>
<p  class="match">The Good Recruitment campaign, created by businesses for businesses, exists to promote 
the critical importance that good recruitment practice plays in organisational success.</p>
<div class="cta-link-bottom"><a href="https://www.rec.uk.com/good-recruitment-campaign">Read more</a></div>
</li>
